  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink42-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">talainiṉṟu oḻukappaṭāniṉṟa parattai talaivaṉ piṟa parattaiyaruṭaṉ oḻukiṉāṉ
          eṉṟu pulantāḷāka, ataṉaiyaṟinta talaivi avaṉ taṉṉillattup pukuntuḻit tāṉ aṟintamai tōṉṟac
          colliyatu.</p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>

      <div xml:id="Aink42">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l> makiḻmikac ciṟappa mayaṅkiṉaḷ kollō</l>
          <l>yāṇa rūraniṉ māṇiḻai yarivai</l>
          <l>kāviri malirniṟai yaṉṉaniṉ</l>
          <l>mārpunaṉi vilakka ṟoṭaṅki yōḷē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">

          <l> While [her] delight/intoxication seriously overflowed, wasn't she confused?</l>
          <l> [Tell me], man from the fertile village! </l>
          <l> Your young lady with the splendid jewels</l>
          <l> has started seriously blocking your chest</l>
          <l> as if it were the Kāviri in full flood. </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
